      "role": "user",
      "content": "That's a helpful summary of the risks. But what about the people who say this is all just hype or science fiction? I've heard some tech leaders argue that focusing on \"existential risk\" is actually dangerous because it just gives governments an excuse to slow down innovation and let other countries win the AI race. How would you respond to that?",
